      <title>中国在美菲行动中升级南海演习</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/china-holds-sea-patrols-as-us-philippines-drill-in-same-region</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国和菲律宾在有争议地区举行海上演习后，中国升级并扩大了在南海的军事演习。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/china-holds-sea-patrols-as-us-philippines-drill-in-same-region</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 00:19:39 GMT</pubDate>
